name: beautiful but wrong
description: Part of our let's keep it real collection: The skies are moving, but under a closer look, the seas have stopped "living". Our waves our gone. Theres a glitch. We wont allow for nature to become a simulation to enjoy it. 20% of the proceeds will go towards protecting our oceans via reeflifefoundation.org. official certificates will be provided to the owner. simple art that gives life to our oceans.
